sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant O as mall-order
  participant P as mall-product
  participant I as mall-inventory
  participant DB1 as mall_order DB
  participant DB2 as mall_inventory DB
  participant S as Seata TC

  O->>S: 开启 GlobalTransactional create-order
  O->>P: 查询 SKU 信息
  O->>I: lock(orderNo, skuId, quantity)
  I->>DB2: 条件更新 available/locked
  I-->>O: 锁定成功
  O->>DB1: 写入 order_info/order_item
  alt 全部成功
    O->>S: 提交全局事务
    S-->>O: 成功
  else 任一步异常
    O->>S: 回滚全局事务
    S->>DB1: 回滚订单写入
    S->>DB2: 回滚库存锁定
  end
